Hopefully I&#39;ve convinced you that a Swing implementation might be a better solution, which in that case you should make use of a Swing `Timer` instead of `Thread`, as Swing is not thread safe

See [Concurrency in Swing](https://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/uiswing/concurrency/index.html) and [How to Use Swing Timers
