            }
        ]
```
...are actually two objects, not just one. So if you want to have exactly the same structure, you have to add two `Activity` objects to the list, not just one: one with &quot;value&quot; set, and one with &quot;type&quot; and &quot;uuid&quot; set.

However the JSON is far from ideal with &quot;value&quot; and &quot;uuid&quot; obviously duplicated (and maybe two entries belonging to the same set of data - which I cannot say for sure with the information given). In case the structure comes from a third party it might be worth the effort to further discuss that structure.

Otherwise you might need additional code to transform the input and/or output to the model you want to really have.

